cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper discusses the vulnerability of deep neural networks to adversarial examples and proposes a method to improve the optimization-based CW attack. This work is closely related to the fields of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and cybersecurity (cs.CR). The proposed method involves incorporating gradients as a constraint, which is a common technique in optimization-based methods in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE).
